                  Gebote Herzog Rudolfs IV. <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__stephan_oeler_QGW_II_I_708">Stephan, dem <roleName type="prof">öler</roleName></rs>, und seiner <rs type="person" ref="#pe__christine_QGW_II_I_864"><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__stephan_oeler_QGW_II_I_708">Hausfrau</roleName> Christein</rs></rs> ½ lb
